   "## Concept: Tool registry\n",
   "\n",
   "Central registry: register at import, collect schemas, dispatch by name.\n",
   "\n",
   "**Harness Agent** implements this subsystem in ``tools/registry.py`, `tools/file_tools.py``. External harnesses differ in scale (tool count, platforms) but share the same architectural slot.\n",
   "\n",
   "| Concern | Harness Agent | Hermes (reference) | OpenClaw (reference) |\n",
   "|---------|---------------|--------------------|----------------------|\n",
   "| This chapter | ``tools/registry.py`, `tools/file_tools.py`` | see architecture docs | workspace/gateway docs |\n",
   "| Entry point | `AIAgent` or CLI | `run_agent.py` / gateway | gateway + workspace |\n"
  ]
 },
 {
  "cell_type": "markdown",
  "metadata": {},
  "source": [
   "## How it works\n",
   "\n",
   "`register()` \u2192 `openai_schemas()` \u2192 `dispatch()`; toolsets filter availability.\n",
   "\n",
   "```mermaid\n",
   "flowchart LR\n",
   "  U[User or scheduler] --> A[AIAgent]\n",
   "  A --> M[Tool registry]\n",
   "```\n",
   "\n",
   "Trace cells below execute real code paths offline where possible.\n"
  ]
